Package: vdr-plugin-skinnopacity
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${vdr:Depends}
Description: nOpacity skin for VDR
 nOpacity is a highly customizable true color skin for the
 on-screen-display (OSD) of the Linux Video Disc Recorder VDR.

